weka.classifiers.collective

Interface RestartableCollectiveClassifier

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Classifier, CollectiveClassifier, java.lang.Comparable, OptionHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvancedCollective, CollectiveNeighbor, SimpleCollective, TwoStageCollective

    public interface RestartableCollectiveClassifier
extends java.lang.Comparable, CollectiveClassifier
    Interface for restartable collective classifiers, i.e., classifiers that use restarts and iterations to improve themselves.
    Version:
    $Revision: 2019 $
    Author:
    FracPete (fracpete at cs dot waikato dot ac dot nz)
